'''金鰺'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Caranx crysos''}}）为[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]][[鱸形目|鱸形目]][[鱸亞目|鱸亞目]][[鲹科|鲹科]][[鲹属|鲹属]]的[[鱼类|鱼类]]。

==分類及命名==
本種首先由[[美國|美國]][[魚類學|魚類學]]家Samuel L. Mitchill在1815年根據從[[美國|美國]][[紐約灣|紐約灣]]水域採集的標本進行科學描述，該標本被指定為模式種。<ref name = "mitch">{{cite journal  | last = Mitchill  | first = S.L.  | title = The fishes of New York described and arranged  | journal=Transactions of the Literary and Philosophical Society of New York  | volume = 1  | pages = 355–492  | publisher=Van Winkle and Wiley  | year = 1815  | url =  }}</ref>他將這種物種命名為''Scomber crysos''，並提出了一個常見的名稱「黃鯖魚」，其學名在拉丁語中意為「黃金」。之後又被歸類在''Caranx''，''Carangoides''或''Paratractus''屬中，但目前被認為是有效的名稱為''Caranx crysos''。<ref name = "fishbase">{{FishBase species | genus = Caranx | species = crysos | year = 2009 | month = May}}</ref>
==分布==
本魚分布於東[[大西洋|大西洋]]區，從[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]至[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]，包括[[地中海|地中海]]西部；西[[大西洋|大西洋]]區，從[[加拿大|加拿大]][[新斯科細亞省|新斯科細亞省]]至[[巴西|巴西]]，包括[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]海域，為亞熱帶海水魚，棲息深度0-100公尺。
==特徵==
本魚體呈橢圓形而側扁，背部和腹部輪廓具有近似相等的凸度和鼻子略尖，<ref name = "FAO">{{cite book | last = Carpenter | first = K.E. (ed.) | title = The living marine resources of the Western Central Atlantic. Volume 3: Bony fishes part 2 (Opistognathidae to Molidae), sea turtles and marine mammals |series= FAO Species Identification Guide for Fishery Purposes and American Society of Ichthyologists and Herpetologists Special Publication No. 5 | publisher=FAO | year = 2002 | location = Rome | pages = 1438 | url = ftp://ftp.fao.org/docrep/fao/009/y4162e/y4162e00.pdf | isbn = 92-5-104827-4 }}</ref>眼睛的後部有發育良好的脂肪眼瞼覆蓋，背鰭2個，背鰭硬棘9枚、背鰭軟條22-25枚、臀鰭硬棘3枚、臀鰭軟條19-21枚，尾鰭叉形，側線明顯，具有短的弓形彎曲，其彎曲部分與第二背鰭的脊柱下方的直線部分相交。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Berry | first = F.H. | title = Scale and scute development of the carangid fish ''Caranx crysos'' (Mitchill)  | journal=Quarterly Journal of the Florida Academy of Sciences | volume = 23 | pages = 59–66 | year = 1960 }}</ref>上頜包含一系列不規則的外犬齒，內帶有小且規則間隔的牙齒，而下頜包含一條小牙齒帶，體長可達70公分，背面藍綠色到橄欖綠色不等，腹部變成銀灰色到黃銅色。稚魚身上通常有7條深色垂直帶。魚鰭的顏色也各不相同，所有的鰭都從昏暗或透明到橄欖綠。

==生態==
[[File:Blue_runner_school.jpg|thumb]]
本魚棲息在沿海海域，會進行洄游，成群活動，以[[魚類|魚類]]、[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]等為食，對[[大西洋|大西洋]]兩岸物種飲食的研究表明了類似的結果。一項[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]研究發現，該物種以魚類為主，以螃蟹，蝦，橈足類和其他小型甲殼類動物為主。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Randall | first = J.E.  | title = Food habits of reef fishes of the West Indies | journal=Studies in Tropical Oceanography  | volume = 5  | pages = 665–847  | year = 1967  | issn = 0081-8720  }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = da Silva Monteiro | first = V.M. | title = Peixes de Cabo Verde  | publisher=Ministério do Mar, Gabinete do Secretário de Estado da Cultura. M2- Artes Gráficas, Lda  | year = 1998  | location = Lisbon  | pages = 179  | isbn = }}</ref>在[[維德角群島|維德角群島]]進行的更詳細的研究，本種以[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]、[[水母|水母]]和其他小型[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]為食。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Mirto | first = S. |author2=M. Bellavia|author3=T. La Rosa | title = Primi dati sulle abitudini alimentari di giovanili di ''Caranx crysos'' nel Golfo di Castellammare (Sicilia nord occidentale) | journal=Biologia Marina Mediterranea | volume = 9 | issue = 1 (Supp.) | pages = 726–728 | year = 2002 | issn = 1123-4245 }}</ref>幼魚以[[浮游動物|浮游動物]]為主要的食物來源。 <ref name = "foodoil">{{cite book | last = Keenan | first = S.F.  |author2=M.C. Benfield| title = Importance of zooplankton in the diets of Blue Runner (''Caranx crysos'') near offshore petroleum platforms in the Northern Gulf of Mexico|series=OCS Study MMS 2003-029  | publisher=Coastal Fisheries Institute, Louisiana State University. U.S. Dept. of the Interior  | year = 2003 | location = New Orleans | pages = 129 | isbn = }}</ref>

==經濟利用==
本魚具有經濟價值的物種。<ref name = "fisheries">{{cite web | last = Fisheries and Agricultural Organisation | title = Global Production Statistics 1950–2007 | work = Blue runner | publisher = FAO | url = http://www.fao.org/figis/servlet/TabSelector | accessdate = 19 May 2009 | archive-date = 2012-05-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120515030053/http://www.fao.org/figis/servlet/TabSelector | dead-url = no }}</ref>在美洲，最近的捕撈數據顯示，正在採集（或報告）的物種數量增加，2006年和2007年捕撈量平均在6000至7000噸之間，而在1980年代和1990年代，每年捕撈量很少超過1000噸。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Tubino | first = R.D. | author2 = C. Monteiro | author3 = L.E.D. Moraes | author4 = E.T. Paes | title = Artisanal fisheries production in the coastal zone of Itaipu, Niteroi, RJ, Brazil | journal = Brazilian Journal of Oceanography | volume = 55 | issue = 3 | pages = 187–197 | year = 2007 | url = http://www.scielo.br/pdf/bjoce/v55n3/v55n3a03.pdf | accessdate = 22 May 2009 | doi = 10.1590/s1679-87592007000300003 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924115032/http://www.scielo.br/pdf/bjoce/v55n3/v55n3a03.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>主要以圍網、刺網和鉤線方法捕獲。在市場上以新鮮，乾燥，煙熏或魚粉，油或誘餌等方式販售。另外本魚對休閒漁業也很重要，垂釣者經常將這些物種用作食物並用作誘餌。目前已知較大的標本在其肉體中驗出[[雪卡毒素|雪卡毒素]]，其中有幾例來自[[維京群島|維京群島]]。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Morris | first = J.G. |author2=P. Lewin |author3=C.W. Smith |author4=P.A. Blake |author5=R. Schneider | title = Ciguatera Fish Poisoning – Epidemiology of the Disease on St. Thomas, United States Virgin Islands | journal=American Journal of Tropical Health and Medicine | volume = 31 | issue = 3 | pages = 574–578 | year = 1982 | issn = 0002-9637 }}</ref>

